    <MissileTemplate>
      <AssociatedTemplateName>SSM-132 Deflector</AssociatedTemplateName>
      <Designation>SSM-132</Designation>
      <Nickname>Deflector</Nickname>
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - $MISSILESEEKER_MODE_ACTIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;RADAR&lt;/color&gt;)/$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;) - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_BLASTFRAG</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SSM-132 Deflector&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 1 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SSM-1 body, which is a nimble space-superiority missile.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_BLASTFRAG warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
